00:00:08.164 --> 00:00:10.580
HAL VARIAN: OK, I'm ready to
do the official introduction.

00:00:10.580 --> 00:00:12.580
I'm Hal Varian and I'm
the chief economist here.

00:00:12.580 --> 00:00:14.080
I think many of you know me.

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:16.079
Glenn Weyl is a
Principal Researcher

00:00:16.079 --> 00:00:20.660
